posts.title: 为何屡发事故 外卖平台的“速度与激情”呢？
posts.text:
摘要：身处高科时代下，我们拥有了享之不尽的便利，得到了前所未有的福利，足不出户就能办很多事。互联网经济的全面到来，我们可以网购、可以虚拟场景、可以点餐……然而经济的快速增长，导致诸多问题也循着空隙跃然眼前。 身处高科时代下，我们拥有了享之不尽的便利，得到了前所未有的福利，足不出户就能办很多事。互联网经济的全面到来，我们可以网购、可以虚拟场景、可以点餐……
然而经济的快速增长，导致诸多问题也循着空隙跃然眼前。近年来，互联网经济增速的显著代表就是电商和外卖两大巨头。尤其是外卖平台的日益走俏成为上班族、学生族等一众年轻者的“团宠”。
据美团外卖官网公布的数据显示，目前美团外卖日接单量可达1200万份。吃饭是人的刚需，外卖平台这个行业可以说是经久不衰，不会受到外界因素冲击。当然这只是客观因素，能影响外卖平台的因素更是不胜枚举，消费者的青睐、食品安全质量等随时可以使外卖平台朝夕溃堤。
食品安全问题引人担忧。 外卖作为“民以食为天”的巨大承载平台，确实是任重道远。屡见报端的食品卫生、商客矛盾也在威胁着外卖市场在餐饮界的宠儿地位。日前，美团外卖员工偷吃食客饭菜并吐回的视频一时之间引发热议。事件发生后，美团外卖官方微博作出道歉回应并称已辞退该骑手。但很明显这种解决方式并没有从根本上消除外卖平台的这种管理漏洞，似乎只是为了给外界一个处理结果而已。
就外卖员偷吃顾客的餐食已经犯了二宗罪。其一，偷吃，侵犯了顾客的个人合法消费权益。饭作为顾客购买的商品，在未经允许、顾客不知情的情况，外卖员却偷吃。其二，外卖员工素质问题有待加强，如果说偷吃属情节轻微，那么偷吃后又吐回饭盒的性质就极为恶劣了。送餐安全问题由此让人不禁深深担忧，我们在订餐时如何知晓自己的餐食未被动过，打开餐盒时，我们还能放心享用吗？中间只有外卖员接触的时间该如何保证透明配送，这个问题不得引人重视，简单的开除员工显然是敷衍了事。
食品安全方面，还将面临送餐源头是否有保障，也就是外卖平台的商家是否具有合格的营业执照及相关食品卫生安全许可。在第三方平台订餐的消费者是根本无法看到现实中的商家店面以及制餐过程。这一环节在外卖平台的监管力度上显然是不尽合乎规范的。曾经被大量曝出的非法小饭馆在外卖平台有着干净整洁的店面，被相关部门查处时却是一片狼藉，挨着厕所的，餐具在地上的、动物粪便附着其中的……这些画面不禁让人作呕。
变相刷单的好评差评。 相信大家点餐时，都会比较关注店铺销量和评分以及用户评价，看了实际的店面照片和餐食图片，确定安全合法、卫生可靠才放心订餐。但不知曾几何时，刷单的方式应运而生，凭着销量、评分优势的“金字招牌”店铺却是空有其表，好评都是人为伪造出的假象，店铺的真实面目又回归到那些“苍蝇鼠馆”。
大量的刷好评与之对立的当然是不允许有差评的存在，然而有消费者本着权益、真实表述餐食问题时，给了差评，受到短信电话威胁、上门报复的更是屡见不鲜。这种事情已经不能单纯的认为是哪一方的过错，外卖市场乱象不由得引起国家相关部门的重视。
国家也对网络食品安全以及外卖平台正式施行了《网络食品安全违法行为查处办法》，这也意味着外卖平台必须担负起监督商家的食品安全等各方面的责任。如何协调好商家、消费者及自身平台良性发展，成为外卖平台应该深耕的问题。
不具人性化的消费者保护利益。 上周才被曝光的饿了么平台存在的不合理霸王条款。消费者在订单下发错误时却不能及时退单，后来是由商家自掏腰包为消费者全额赔付，其中包括饿了么平台的抽成费。外卖平台固然是完美连接了线上线下订餐者，抽取一定的平台费用是合理合法合规，但作为二大巨头之一，霸王条款的出现有些垄断的嫌疑，商家的利益得不到保障，同时也违背 了 消费用户的自主选择权。
吃着 “空头响”的饿了么此一番行为，如若引不起重视，消费者倒戈相向、商家退出平台也不是没可能，作为消费一方的用户或是收益一方的商家，利益是决定选择的关键，给予彼此更大的选择空间才能获得外卖平台的长久利益。
频出事故的外卖平台，安全卫生显然是社会聚焦问题。在做好规范整治安全卫生的同时，抓好偏门偏道的不正当手段，促进外卖市场良性竞争也将是外卖平台要面临的重要课题。

posts.title: Puma integrates Indian graffiti, street dance and hip hop in four languages to woo millennials
posts.text:
Creative Works By Taruka Srivastav - 07 November 2017 05:56am 
As part of a hyper local language promotion strategy for its range Puma Suede, Puma has rolled out its latest campaign 'Suede Gully' where it portrays the street culture of India to woo millennials. 
Conceptualized by DDB Mudra , the film captures together three street art forms - namely graffiti, rap and dance - and showcases those through eight rappers, seven street artists and 36 hip-hop dancers from Mumbai, Delhi, Shillong and Madurai. 
The ‘Suede Gully’ street anthem is composed by Sneha Khanwalkar and directed by Sasha Rainbow and features four different languages– Hindi, Tamil, Punjabi and Khasi. The video alternates between the artists who are transforming the streets fuses into a single rap. The video also features actress Disha Patani. 
The dance crews are led by Mukti Mohan and features the Bengaluru-based Black Ice Crew, Shillong’s Unity One Crew, Mumbai’s Beast Mode Crew and Delhi’s Higher Vision Crew. Also, featuring are Indian street artists, Shilo Shiv Suleman, Baadal Nanjundaswamy, Indian Artist crew and Anpu Varkey. Representing Indian rap and hip hop are Bombay’s Divine, Delhi’s Prabhdeep, Shillong’s rap crew Khasi Bloodz and Madurai's Madurai Souljour. 
Debosmita Majumder, head of marketing, Puma (India) said: “Today’s youth have taken to modern forms of self-expression, giving rise to a new generation of creators. They use the streets as a canvas to express themselves through various forms of art, music and dance. For the first time in India, PUMA is bringing these diverse art forms on a single platform – Suede Gully. Suede Gully is our attempt to bring to the forefront the true essence of Indian street culture.” 
Vishnu Srivatsav, creative head, DDB Mudra South said: “Puma’s Suede has always been a voice of street culture and Suede Gully looks to bring to life the incredibly unique and diverse culture and expression of our very own gullies. It’s art, its music, its culture and it’s fashion. So many people, folks who live for their art, from different corners of the country, bringing their awesome talents to collaborate on this platform, that’s really special.”

"Other concerns I have with this are that perverts can get the pictures and use them pornographically and when uploading pictures of anyone besides yourself you're responsible for every pervert that accesses those images even if you never find out about it and I hate the thought of that so I'd rather not take the chance of having to live with it"
I'm sorry, but quite regardless of your own excellent reasons for not wanting photos online, this bit is judgemental.
If this is something people shouldn't be able to "live with", what's so special about photos online? Should there be no images of children anywhere? in books, in papers, in adverts? What about a paedo who gets a sexual kick out of watching your child in the supermarket queue- can you live with that? Once you start holding yourself responsible for other people's perverted desires, where does it end?
I wholly agree with any measure that is designed to actually protect an individual child from actual contact with paedophiles or other abusers. But suggesting that parents are responsible if a paedo catches sight of their child, whether through a picture or in RL, is just one step too far. Paedos are responsible for paedos.

posts.text: 内閣府は、「高齢社会対策の基本的在り方等に関する検討会」の報告書を公表した。認知症の高齢者の増加を踏まえ、「QOL（生活の質）の議論を進め、分野横断的な基本方針等を定めることができないか」などと提案している。【新井哉】 新しい高齢社会対策大綱の案の作成に役立てようと、検討会は、重点課題などを議論し、報告書をまとめた。 報告書では、▽医療、介護、食、住まいなどの必要性が満たされる環境の整備▽介護離職ゼロの実現▽人生の最終段階の過ごし方▽後見制度―といった高齢者の活躍の支障となる問題について、「環境整備や先進技術の活用を進めていくことが重要」とした。 中長期的には、高齢期の健康寿命の延伸などが考えられるとし、AI（人工知能）などの技術革新に基づいたサービスが創出される可能性を指摘。また、介護予防や健康改善、医療費適正化といった「具体的なゴール達成」には、ビッグデータの分析を活用する必要性を挙げた。 CBnews

Hrmph. 
So, I put the eggs and milk back into the fridge and went to make my "coffee". 
nd. 
Insert large wail. 
And, a couple of expletives for good measure. 
I have no idea what happened to my shopping list this week, but it was obviously written in my sleep! 
:( 
Peppermint tea and toast later, I headed out to spend the morning with one of my beautiful woman friends, and subsequently spent the morning talking non stop, coming up with solutions for World Peace, and generally setting the world to rights. 
Oh, and, writing a thoroughly comprehensive shopping list for my next trip to the supermarket. 
!! 
However, my day was still set to challenge me in a Seriously First World Problem kind of way, when, this afternoon, having spent and agonising hour deciding on my top choice for a colour scheme for my next Blanket Project, I was seriously annoyed and ridiculously disappointed to discover that TWO of the gorgeous colours I had chosen were NOT any where near full balls of yarn. 
Meaning, I have two choices. 
One. 
Pick another colour combination that will use some of the dozens of other FULL balls of yarn. 
Or two. 
The thing is, I really, really love the colours I decided upon. 
Wail. 
Again. 
Sigh. 
I know I should simply make one of my other colour combinations, and when I have used up some of the excessive amount of yarn in my stash, then I can order some more. 
But, I was feeling so excited about the colours I had chosen and, now, I seem to have lost the impetus to make another blanket at all. 
Yes, I am a fickle being. 
Sigh. 
So, in light of this annoying situation, and in an attempt to stop stalling and Get On With It, I think I shall simply begin making crochet squares from ALL the balls of yarn, using all the colours I have and several different crochet patterns and, then I can sit and decide upon colour combinations and join squares into blankets later. 
Having decided this, I feel relieved that I will be using all my yarn up, instead of spending more money (not a good idea AT ALL, and let's face it completely defeats the purpose of this exercise!!) and wasting time agonising over colour combinations and yarn availability. 
Choices.

posts.text:
输卵管疏通后怀不上，绝大多数情况是因为疏通效果不理想，没有彻底疏通输卵管，或是卵巢、子宫、内分泌、精子精液等其他生育环节出了问题。总结下来不外乎这两种原因。
1、疏通效果不理想
正常的输卵管由子宫端至伞部长约8—15厘米，管径为0.1—1厘米。如果疏通手术不彻底或者影响了宫腔内的纤毛蠕动，也会导致卵子和精子无法相遇而不怀孕。
输卵管疏通成功率受到医疗技术、医疗设施的先进程度和手术医生的技术经验等影响，因此手术后能否怀孕，选择专业不孕不育医院是关键。
如果手术没有做好，导致输卵管没有完全疏通，或是手术过程中对输卵管及其邻近器官造成损伤，都可能会导致手术后怀不上。
2、其他生育环节病变
由于生理疾病、精神压力、生活环境、生活习惯、年龄等因素的影响，除了输卵管问题之外，很多育龄人群的生殖健康都出了问题。
女性年龄越大，生育能力越差，因为据临床资料显示，女性年龄越大，多囊卵巢综合征、子宫疾病、内分泌失调等疾病发病率就越高。
和女性一样，男性精子精液异常、睾丸炎症、精索静脉曲张、前列腺炎等疾病的发病率也随着年龄增长而逐渐升高，导致男性患上不育症，使女性无法受孕。
疏通后还是不怀孕怎么办?
如果输卵管疏通手术后超过半年没怀孕，男女双方都要及时到医院检查，男方检查精子精液数量和质量;女方除了检查输卵管手术效果之外，还应检查卵巢、子宫和激素等重要生育环节是否正常，这样才能全面准确地找出不怀孕的原因，对症治疗。

posts.text:
Prémios aos vencedores do quiz sobre a biblioteca Este ano a  International Association of School Librarianship  (IASL) propôs, como anualmente acontece, o tema aglutinador —  Ligando Comunidades e Culturas  (tradução adotada pela RBE), tendo sido elaborado um cartaz de divulgação da efeméride, comum a todas as bibliotecas do agrupamento.  
Este período foi aproveitado para reforçar a visibilidade da biblioteca escolar e a consciencialização acerca do seu valor nas aprendizagens, tendo as turmas do 7º ano (8 turmas/182 alunos) e respetivos professores (13 professores) sido acolhidos, no auditório pequeno da ESA, pelas professoras Adelaide Peres e Mónica Candoso que, através da apresentação em prezi,  do quiz/jogo na plataforma kahoot! ( com recurso ao telemóvel e prémios aos vencedores) e do visionamento do pequeno filme “Mr. Bean na biblioteca” , lhes deram a conhecer melhor este espaço, a sua orgânica (nomeadamente o programa Prisma e a organização do fundo documental pela Classificação Decimal Universal - CDU) e as regras de funcionamento, tentando promover a sua utilização. Também lhes deram a conhecer o blogue, sua utilidade e  funcionalidades.  Esta atividade procurou ser enriquecedora para os novos utilizadores conhecerem melhor a BE, a PB e equipa, bem como os seus recursos e regras de utilização, organização e funcionamento.
